SUM(CASE WHEN invoices.is_loss_of_receivables = 0 THEN lines.amount ELSE 0 END) as total_net,
SUM(CASE WHEN invoices.is_loss_of_receivables = 0 THEN lines.tax ELSE 0 END) as total_tax,
